item.title: Can someone help me code some stuff into my sever or atleast telll me how tocode
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

[quote=“Anfernio, post:18, topic:261918”]Ugh.

if(objectID == 75){ addItem(995, 1000000); addItem(6585, 1); toX = 2789; toY = 4722; sM("Congratulations. You have been rewarded 1 million gold pieces."); sM("And a fury? The look on your face must be :O!!!!"); sM("Now you need to find a...portal? Hmmm, This is interesting..."); cabbagefield(); }

cabbagefield(); opens up my interface, it’d be like this if you wanted to open up the quest menu that opens…

public void cabbagefield() { sendQuest("@dre@The Cabbage Field Song.", 8144); clearQuestInterface(); sendQuest("@gre@DO NOT CLOSE THIS UNTIL YOU'VE READ IT!", 8147); sendQuest("The cabbage field, field, field, field..", 8148); sendQuest("Scarecrow haunts this field. Poor little Jimmy...", 8149); sendQuest("He's been dared to eat the cabbage! Ulp goes the cabbage!", 8150); sendQuest("Ulp goes two! Ulp goes three!", 8151); sendQuest("@cya@You suddenly remember this song!", 8152); sendQuestSomething(8143); showInterface(8134); flushOutStream(); }[/quote]
But that’s a method that activates when you click a global object.
He is trying to activate a case when he clicks a tab on the emote tab.
